The files here are read various times when the bot msg's
you some help for ident, new users, etc.

badhost
   identing a user

banner
   connecting to the bot

files
   joining the file secion

intro
   welcoming a new user

newbot
   when first msg'ing your bot hello

newbot-limbo
   when first starting up a limbo bot

newuser
   new user telneting onto the bot
